<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li>99 bugs. Sample response: <m>62 + 11 + 19 + 7 = ?</m><m>11 + 19 = 30</m><m>30 + 62 = 92</m><m>92 + 7 = 99</m></li>
      <li>53 more. Sample response: <m>61-8</m> is <m>61-1-7</m>, which is 53.</li>
      <li>51 fewer. Sample response: <m>62-11 = 51</m></li>
      <li>Sample response: How many of the bugs were spiders or beetles?</li>
      <li>Sample response: 26 of the bugs were spiders or beetles. <m>7 + 19 = 6 + 1 + 19</m>, which is 26.</li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


